<h2>How Left Right Works</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>
After every tee shot, teams are created based on ball position.
</p>

<ul>
<li>The two balls farthest left become partners</li>
<li>The two balls farthest right become partners</li>
</ul>

<p>
The teams change almost every hole.
</p>

<p>
Usually played as best ball with one team paying the other.
</p>

<p>
Aggressive players can end up on the same side creating huge swings.
</p>

</div>

